  "detailed_description": "Build mechas, command your squad members to victory and conquest, seize the stars, settle randomized unknown star systems, defend your faction from hordes of assailants.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607740/extras/00de34786bf855fd034e16f89ae5eb59.poster.avif?t=1680102633\" width=640 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607740/extras/00de34786bf855fd034e16f89ae5eb59.webm?t=1680102633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607740/extras/00de34786bf855fd034e16f89ae5eb59.mp4?t=1680102633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About:</h2>-All actions avaliable to your mechas depend on the choice of parts for every mecha in your squad.<br>-Diferent mecha parts grant different abilities and stats.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607740/extras/013ba247dfba6b3611ebd6e51022cb74.poster.avif?t=1680102633\" width=507 height=773 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1607740/extras/013ba247dfba6b3611ebd6e51022cb74.webm?t=1680102633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>-Every Ability has a set of effects(damage,movement,buffs).<br>-Every Ability targets differently with selectable targets or directional or area of effects.<br>-Every round mechas roll initiatives(1d20 + Initiative) whoever rolls higher acts first.<br>-Every act has a AP and a EP cost, Powerful skills will cost more.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring:</h2>-Randomized enemy squads.<br>-Randomized star systems.<br>-Grid based Combat.<br>-Local 2-Players versus mode.<br><br>Feel free to send suggestions, complaints and questions to <a href=\"mailto:nullbudgetgames@gmail.com\">nullbudgetgames@gmail.com</a>",
